These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-1::.
There 7 different types of food: grapefruit, blueberry, zucchini, cucumber, pumpkin, pepper, plum
There are 7 different nationalities: japanese, chinese, argentine, british, australian, thai, malaysian
 1. the person eating zucchini is on the far left##1
 2. the person eating cucumber is not the thai##6
 3. the japanese is on the left of the person eating blueberry##1
 4. the malaysian is somewhere to the right of the australian##5
 5. the person eating pumpkin is on the left or right of the person eating plum##3
 6. the japanese is on the right of the person eating zucchini##1
 7. the person eating pepper is somewhere between the person eating blueberry and the chinese##7
 8. the chinese is on the left of the malaysian##1
 9. the british is somewhere between the person eating pumpkin and the argentine##7
10. the argentine is on the left or right of the japanese##3
11. the australian is on the far left##1
12. the person eating cucumber is somewhere to the left of the malaysian##5
13. the person eating cucumber is somewhere to the right of the person eating pepper##5
14. the person eating plum is somewhere to the right of the person eating pumpkin##5
15. the person eating pumpkin is the chinese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4     |     5     |     6     |    7    |
| Food          | zucchini    | grapefruit    | blueberry | pepper | cucumber | pumpkin    | plum |
| Nationality   | australian | japanese | argentine  | thai   | british    | chinese | malaysian |

