.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-2::.
There 7 different types of food: cauliflower, lime, lettuce, blueberry, papaya, apricot, potato
The people have 7 different hobbies: sudoku, collecting, magic-tricks, traveling, board-games, dancing, reading
 1. the person who's hobby is dancing is somewhere between the person eating potato and the person eating lime##7
 2. the person who's hobby is reading is the person eating blueberry##1
 3. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
 4. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the person eating apricot##1
 5. the person eating cauliflower is somewhere between the person who's hobby is traveling and the person who's hobby is collecting##7
 6. the person eating apricot is somewhere between the person eating blueberry and the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##7
 7. the person eating papaya is somewhere between the person eating blueberry and the person eating lime##7
 8. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
 9. the person who's hobby is board-games is somewhere to the left of the person eating papaya##5
10. the person eating papaya is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##5
11. the person who's hobby is dancing is not the person eating potato##6
12. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
13. the person who's hobby is board-games is between the person who's hobby is traveling and the person eating blueberry##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |       5       |      6      |    7    |
| Food    | potato  | lettuce | apricot | blueberry | cauliflower     | papaya | lime  |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks | dancing | collecting  | reading  | board-games | traveling      | sudoku |

