 3. the fan of classical is not the person who's hobby is fishing##6
 4. the fan of folk is somewhere to the right of the fan of salsa##5
 5. the fan of folk is between the fan of salsa and the person who's hobby is chess##2
 6. the fan of house is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##5
 7. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the far right##1
 8. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left or right of the fan of soul##3
 9. the person who's hobby is singing is somewhere between the fan of trance and the fan of disco##7
10. the fan of classical is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is reading##3
11. the person who's hobby is chess is in an even position##4
12. the person who's hobby is chess is not the fan of folk##6
13. the person who's hobby is camping is somewhere between the person who's hobby is reading and the person who's hobby is chess##7
14. the fan of soul is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is chess##3
15. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is chess##3
16. the person who's hobby is chess is not the fan of salsa##6
17. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left or right of the fan of house##3
18. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
19. the fan of folk is somewhere to the left of the fan of trance##5

.:: Answer ::.
