 6. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the person driving the car##1
 7. the person driving the bus is somewhere between the person driving the car and the person driving the airplane##7
 8. the person who's sport is rollering is on the far left##1
 9. the person driving the airplane is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is cycling##5
10. the person who's sport is surfing is in an even position##4
11. the person who's sport is surfing is somewhere between the person who's sport is badminton and the person who's sport is weightlifting##7
12. the person driving the roller is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##5
13. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
14. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is somewhere to the left of the person driving the train##5
15. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left or right of the person driving the roller##3
16. the person driving the airplane is somewhere to the left of the person driving the bus##5
17. the person driving the roller is between the person who's sport is surfing and the person driving the helicopter##2
18. the person who's sport is badminton is not the person driving the train##6
